2
00:00:12,790 --> 00:00:14,720
( Eugeo sighs )

3
00:00:16,260 --> 00:00:17,590
( Girl sighs )

4
00:00:17,660 --> 00:00:18,590
Hello.

5
00:00:21,400 --> 00:00:23,300
We are--i mean...

6
00:00:23,360 --> 00:00:26,370
I am fizel, a sister-in-training
of the church.

7
00:00:26,430 --> 00:00:28,100
How do?

8
00:00:28,170 --> 00:00:31,570
And this timid little thing
is my fellow sister-in-training.

9
00:00:31,640 --> 00:00:33,140
Linel: Uh, i’m linel.

10
00:00:33,210 --> 00:00:35,340
Fizel: We heard
there were intruders

11
00:00:35,410 --> 00:00:37,650
from the dark territory
lurking about.

12
00:00:37,710 --> 00:00:39,210
Are you they?

13
00:00:39,280 --> 00:00:40,310
Eugeo: Huh?

14
00:00:42,220 --> 00:00:44,450
kirito: I think
i’ll let you handle this one.

15
00:00:44,520 --> 00:00:46,390
They look annoying.

16
00:00:47,690 --> 00:00:49,590
( Eugeo sighs )

17
00:00:49,660 --> 00:00:51,530
Um, we are, sort of.

18
00:00:51,590 --> 00:00:53,630
