from the human realm,

19
00:00:53,700 --> 00:00:55,300
not the dark territory.

20
00:00:55,360 --> 00:00:59,970
As for intruding here,
I guess we are, technically.

21
00:01:01,100 --> 00:01:03,000
( Girls sigh )

22
00:01:03,070 --> 00:01:04,570
Fizel: Well, nel? Do these two

23
