look anything
like monsters to you? Huh?

24
00:01:08,340 --> 00:01:10,010
where are
their horns and tails?

25
00:01:10,080 --> 00:01:11,550
Linel: But how should I know?

26
00:01:11,610 --> 00:01:14,480
I was just telling you what
the book said they looked like.

27
00:01:14,550 --> 00:01:17,220
