jumping to conclusions, zel.

28
00:01:17,290 --> 00:01:18,390
Eugeo: Uh, ladies...

29
00:01:19,450 --> 00:01:20,690
We’ll go.

30
00:01:20,760 --> 00:01:22,590
If someone sees us,
you’ll get in trouble.

31
00:01:25,160 --> 00:01:26,430
( Girls giggle )

32
00:01:28,330 --> 00:01:31,200
Fizel: Don’t worry. There’s
no chance of that happening.

33
00:01:31,270 --> 00:01:32,630
This morning, the church ordered

34
00:01:32,700 --> 00:01:34,540
all the monks, nuns,
and apprentices

35
00:01:34,600 --> 00:01:37,340
to stay in their quarters
and lock their doors.

36
00:01:37,410 --> 00:01:40,610
This was the perfect opportunity
for us to sneak out

37
00:01:40,680 --> 00:01:43,310
