at these nasty intruders.

38
00:01:43,380 --> 00:01:45,180
Eh? ( Grunts )

39
00:01:45,250 --> 00:01:46,180
Huh.

40
00:01:46,250 --> 00:01:48,050
( Eugeo sighs )

41
00:01:48,120 --> 00:01:49,350
Fizel: They’re human.

42
00:01:49,420 --> 00:01:51,120
- Linel: Yes, very.
- ( Eugeo chuckles )

43
