or knights of darkness.

49
00:02:05,270 --> 00:02:08,470
I’m sure you can understand why
we were so curious about you.

50
00:02:08,540 --> 00:02:11,210
( Eugeo sighs ) Huh?

51
00:02:12,310 --> 00:02:13,940
Linel: One last thing,

52
00:02:14,010 --> 00:02:15,980
do you mind telling us
what your names are?

53
00:02:18,250 --> 00:02:20,380
Eugeo: Eh, not at all.

54
00:02:20,450 --> 00:02:23,580
i’m eugeo,
and this here is kirito.

55
00:02:23,650 --> 00:02:24,990
- ( Kirito groans )
- Linel: Huh.

56
00:02:25,050 --> 00:02:27,320
Do you not have last names?

57
00:02:27,390 --> 00:02:30,320
eugeo: No.
My family are settlers.

58
00:02:30,390 --> 00:02:32,360
And do you have last names?

59
00:02:32,430 --> 00:02:36,030
Linel: Yes. We’ve been waiting
to share them with you.

60
00:02:36,100 --> 00:02:37,130
Eugeo: Uh...

61
00:02:37,200 --> 00:02:38,530
- ( Blade stabs )
- ( Groaning )

