within minutes.

249
00:13:50,340 --> 00:13:54,240
the pontifex,
using her holy skills,

250
00:13:54,310 --> 00:13:57,980
fused the 1,000 mirrors
together,

251
00:13:58,050 --> 00:14:01,820
then honed them
to create a magnificent sword...

252
00:14:02,950 --> 00:14:04,890
♪

253
00:14:08,090 --> 00:14:12,130
this sword,
the heaven-piercing blade.

254
00:14:12,190 --> 00:14:15,660
Know this. Your stomach and foot
were punctured

255
00:14:15,730 --> 00:14:19,130
by the glorious power
of the sun god, solus.

256
00:14:19,200 --> 00:14:22,070
Kirito: It reflects
the sun’s energy.

257
00:14:24,140 --> 00:14:28,340
Fanatio: Now, sinner,
prepare to meet your end.

258
00:14:30,450 --> 00:14:31,910
Kirito: Discharge!

259
00:14:34,180 --> 00:14:36,020
( Groans )

260
00:14:37,320 --> 00:14:39,290
( Fanatio groans )

261
00:14:44,530 --> 00:14:45,790
( Gasps )

262
00:14:45,860 --> 00:14:48,130
( Both gasp )

263
00:14:50,400 --> 00:14:53,330
♪

264
00:14:53,400 --> 00:14:56,070
fanatio:
Don’t you dare look at me.

265
00:14:57,540 --> 00:15:01,040
your eyes
are laced with disdain,

266
00:15:01,110 --> 00:15:04,350
just like the commander’s!

267
00:15:04,410 --> 00:15:08,520
you men think my gender
affects the quality of my skill.

268
00:15:08,580 --> 00:15:10,890
Even sinners deny me respect!

269
00:15:10,950 --> 00:15:13,290
i command you
to fight me in earnest!

270
00:15:16,620 --> 00:15:20,360
I am a knight,
an integrity knight!

271
00:15:20,430 --> 00:15:22,500
( Kirito groaning )

272
00:15:22,560 --> 00:15:25,270
( Fanatio groaning )

273
00:15:25,330 --> 00:15:28,200
Kirito: I get it.
Your sword and skill,

274
00:15:28,270 --> 00:15:29,370
it’s a cover.

275
00:15:29,440 --> 00:15:31,870
They let you stand back
and fire shots

276
00:15:31,940 --> 00:15:33,510
and hide the fact
you’re a woman.

277
00:15:33,580 --> 00:15:37,180
Ain’t that right, lady fanatio?!

278
00:15:38,250 --> 00:15:39,380
Fanatio: How dare you?!

279
00:15:39,450 --> 00:15:41,180
Kirito: Just so you know,

280
00:15:41,250 --> 00:15:43,350
the reason I looked
so shocked before,

281
00:15:43,420 --> 00:15:45,190
it wasn’t ’cause you’re a woman.

282
00:15:45,250 --> 00:15:47,060
it’s ’cause,
when you lost your helmet,

283
00:15:47,120 --> 00:15:48,390
you lost all your nerve.

284
00:15:48,460 --> 00:15:51,360
I know why you hide your face
under that helmet.

285
00:15:51,430 --> 00:15:55,460
If anyone here’s got a problem
with you bein’ a woman,

286
00:15:55,530 --> 00:15:56,460
it’s you.

287
00:15:56,530 --> 00:15:57,900
( Fanatio growls )

288
00:15:57,970 --> 00:16:00,100
Silence! You wretch!

289
00:16:00,170 --> 00:16:01,100
I shall kill you!

290
00:16:01,170 --> 00:16:03,270
Kirito: You wanna try, go ahead!

291
00:16:03,340 --> 00:16:06,540
I know what it’s like
to fight and lose to women,

292
00:16:06,610 --> 00:16:07,980
and you know what?

293
00:16:08,040 --> 00:16:09,940
I never held back for them,

294
00:16:10,010 --> 00:16:11,950
and I won’t for you! ( Grunts )

295
00:16:12,010 --> 00:16:14,180
( Growls )

296
00:16:14,250 --> 00:16:16,180
♪

297
00:16:23,660 --> 00:16:26,130
( Woman vocalizing )

298
00:16:30,300 --> 00:16:31,600
( Kirito sighs )

299
00:16:31,670 --> 00:16:33,130
( Fanatio chuckles )

300
00:16:36,000 --> 00:16:37,270
Eugeo: No way.

301
00:16:45,910 --> 00:16:47,580
( Both yell )

302
00:16:54,320 --> 00:16:55,460
Fanatio: I was wrong.

303
00:16:55,520 --> 00:16:57,160
♪

304
00:16:57,230 --> 00:16:58,530
You are different.

305
00:16:58,590 --> 00:17:01,430
Although you may be a sinner,
you are quite unlike

306
00:17:01,500 --> 00:17:03,330
the other men
I have fought before.

307
00:17:05,000 --> 00:17:06,930
None of them had your spirit.

308
00:17:07,000 --> 00:17:08,940
their attacks
all lacked conviction

309
00:17:09,000 --> 00:17:10,940
once they saw
my detestable face.

310
00:17:11,010 --> 00:17:13,910
Kirito: "Detestable"? Okay...

311
00:17:13,980 --> 00:17:15,880
Then how come you comb your hair

312
00:17:15,940 --> 00:17:18,280
and put on lipstick
if you wear a helmet?

313
00:17:18,350 --> 00:17:20,580
You don’t do it for yourself.
That’s for sure.

314
00:17:20,650 --> 00:17:22,350
( Fanatio scoffs )

315
00:17:22,420 --> 00:17:24,490
♪

316
00:17:28,590 --> 00:17:30,360
Kirito: You’re bitter,
’cause you can’t have

317
00:17:30,430 --> 00:17:32,460
the person you love,
and you know why?

318
00:17:32,530 --> 00:17:35,330
it’s ’cause the church
and the pontifex say you can’t.

319
00:17:35,400 --> 00:17:37,060
Well, i’m here to destroy ’em

320
00:17:37,130 --> 00:17:39,900
and free everyone
from their tyranny!

321
00:17:39,970 --> 00:17:42,440
fanatio: I can tell
you are no agent of darkness,

322
00:17:42,500 --> 00:17:44,940
as the prime minister claimed.

323
00:17:45,010 --> 00:17:47,610
Regardless, you are
still extremely dangerous.

324
00:17:47,680 --> 00:17:50,980
You would disrupt the church
and the knighthood,

325
00:17:51,050 --> 00:17:54,320
not just with your sword,
but with your words.

326
00:17:54,380 --> 00:17:57,890
you also put
the human empire in peril,

327
00:17:57,950 --> 00:18:01,390
and that, sir,
is a knight’s duty to protect.

328
00:18:01,460 --> 00:18:06,190
you speak the truth,
but I am obliged to defeat you,

329
00:18:06,260 --> 00:18:09,300
even if it sullies
my pride as a knight!

330
00:18:09,360 --> 00:18:12,230
hidden light
of the heaven-piercing blade,

331
00:18:12,300 --> 00:18:14,340
cast off your shackles!

332
00:18:14,400 --> 00:18:17,110
Release recollection!

333
00:18:27,620 --> 00:18:29,880
( Kirito groaning )

334
00:18:34,420 --> 00:18:35,520
( Gasps )

335
00:18:35,590 --> 00:18:36,990
( Woman gasps )

336
00:18:40,960 --> 00:18:42,400
Kirito: You idiot.

337
00:18:42,460 --> 00:18:44,100
( Gasps )

338
00:18:44,170 --> 00:18:46,070
You’re gonna kill us all!

339
00:18:49,370 --> 00:18:51,270
Eugeo: Now’s my chance,

340
00:18:51,340 --> 00:18:53,540
my only chance!

341
00:18:53,610 --> 00:18:56,610
Enhance armament!

342
00:18:59,580 --> 00:19:01,980
( Woman gasping )

343
00:19:02,050 --> 00:19:03,350
( Grunts ) No--

344
00:19:04,420 --> 00:19:06,120
eugeo: Blue Rose! Bloom!

345
00:19:08,360 --> 00:19:09,520
( Fanatio gasps )

346
00:19:09,590 --> 00:19:11,290
Damn that brat!

347
00:19:11,360 --> 00:19:13,030
( Gasps )

348
00:19:21,140 --> 00:19:22,070
( Kirito groans )

349
00:19:22,140 --> 00:19:23,140
Eugeo: Kirito!

350
00:19:23,200 --> 00:19:24,910
Are you hurt?! Don’t move!

351
00:19:24,970 --> 00:19:25,910
I’ll heal you!

352
00:19:25,970 --> 00:19:26,910
Kirito: I’m fine!

353
00:19:26,980 --> 00:19:29,480
Don’t let up! Keep at it!

354
00:19:29,540 --> 00:19:31,450
She’s tough.

355
00:19:32,580 --> 00:19:34,480
This ain’t enough to stop her!

356
00:19:37,150 --> 00:19:38,350
( Groans )

357
00:19:40,920 --> 00:19:42,360
System call.

358
00:19:44,090 --> 00:19:45,360
( Eugeo gasps )

359
00:19:48,030 --> 00:19:50,500
♪

360
00:19:51,970 --> 00:19:53,600
You knights,

361
00:19:53,670 --> 00:19:55,270
you’re all the same!

362
00:19:55,340 --> 00:19:58,010
You’re all heartless!

363
00:20:08,220 --> 00:20:09,920
Stop fighting!

364
00:20:09,980 --> 00:20:11,190
Stop or die!

365
00:20:11,250 --> 00:20:12,190
( Gasps )

366
00:20:20,160 --> 00:20:22,200
It’s no use.

367
00:20:22,260 --> 00:20:23,260
I can’t win.

368
00:20:23,330 --> 00:20:26,430
I can’t beat her.

369
00:20:26,500 --> 00:20:29,170
Kirito: You’re letting hate
get the better of you, eugeo.

370
00:20:29,240 --> 00:20:30,170
Stop it.

371
00:20:33,240 --> 00:20:35,040
You didn’t come this far

372
00:20:35,110 --> 00:20:38,150
’cause you hated
the integrity knights, did you?

373
00:20:38,210 --> 00:20:41,350
You’re here to get Alice back.

374
00:20:41,420 --> 00:20:43,350
You’re here ’cause you love her.

375
00:20:43,420 --> 00:20:44,450
But guess what.

376
00:20:44,520 --> 00:20:46,490
That integrity knight
over there,

377
00:20:46,550 --> 00:20:48,920
she feels just as strong
about her duty,

378
00:20:48,990 --> 00:20:51,090
and i’m no different.

379
00:20:51,160 --> 00:20:53,230
i wanna protect
everyone in this world--

380
00:20:53,290 --> 00:20:56,000
you, Alice,

381
00:20:56,060 --> 00:20:58,170
even this knight.

382
00:20:58,230 --> 00:21:00,140
We’re so close,

383
00:21:00,200 --> 00:21:02,340
and we can’t afford
to give up now.

384
00:21:04,140 --> 00:21:06,610
Ain’t that right, eugeo?

385
00:21:07,980 --> 00:21:09,180
( Eugeo sighs )

386
00:21:13,920 --> 00:21:18,020
Kirito: Enhance armament!

387
00:21:18,090 --> 00:21:22,090
Singer: ♪ oh, everything
turns to ash, to ash ♪

388
00:21:22,160 --> 00:21:24,090
( Singing in Japanese )

389
00:21:31,600 --> 00:21:35,100
♪ and everything
turns to dust, to dust ♪

390
00:21:35,170 --> 00:21:37,100
( Singing in Japanese )

391
00:21:44,710 --> 00:22:02,430
♪ Forget-me-not

